# PrairieLog — read the vault first

All agent context lives in `D:\Development\AI Workspace\projects\log-stream-service\`:

- `index.md` — start here every session: workflow, contract gate, verification tiers, first-reads by task type.
- `rules.md` — coding rules; read the section matching what you're editing: § Backend (Spring/OpenAPI/security/tests), § Frontend (vanilla/state/docs security), § Release deploy docs (env/CORS/SDK/README), § Meta (maintaining these files).
- `roles.md` — capability roles (router, planner, core-data, infra, backend/frontend feature, integration, reviewer).
